cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the representation and processing of 3D shapes using 2D convolutional neural networks. This falls under the broad category of computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of neural networks for classification and segmentation tasks also suggests the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE).
